Headline::::Prime Minister Narendra Modi Greets Nation On Maha Shivratri



DateTime::::2016-03-07T13:18:19+05:30



New Delhi:                             Prime Minister Narendra Modi today extended his greetings to the people on Maha Shivratri.
"Maha Shivratri greetings to everyone," PM Modi tweeted.
महाशिवरात्रि की हार्दिक शुभकामनाएं।Maha Shivratri greetings to everyone.
- Narendra Modi (@narendramodi) March 7, 2016
Maha Shivratri, celebrated annually in reverence of Lord Shiva, falls on the 13th night and 14th day of Phalguna month or Maagh as per Hindu almanac.
                 



